{"tid":1188413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本史上最大毒案】靜岡縣檢獲1噸「覺醒劑」 7中國人被捕","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T11:22:18.000Z","uid":28195,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a75dceb964681dd2979e3f85628833fd503eb701","tid":1188413,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:51:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vc_8eQjgd_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVc_8eQjgd_M&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=b30826a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vc_8eQjgd_M</a><br />\n<br />\n日本東京警視廳宣佈，當局於本月3日晚上9時半左右，在靜岡縣南伊豆町海岸的一艘可疑船隻上，發現並查獲近1噸重的「覺醒劑」，數量為歷年來最大。7名中國籍男子涉嫌違反《覺醒劑取締法》被捕。<br />\n<br />\n日本警方指，這些毒品分別裝在數百個袋子裏，每袋重約2千克。日本警方認為，疑犯正在海上交收藥物，正就是否涉及國際性走私組織作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n日本認定的「覺醒劑」毒品，包括苯丙胺及甲基苯丙胺，即港人所知的安非他命。<br />\n<br />\n日本財務省稱，此前，日本單次毒品檢獲量之最，是2016年在沖繩縣那霸市一艘遊艇中發現約600公斤毒品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190605/59680169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190605%2F59680169&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=834e3f27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190605%2F59680169&h=875b9284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190605/59680169</a>"},{"pid":"dfff252d0b07c9ac1aac354fe63faf626510cbb8","tid":1188413,"uid":33077,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"即係冰<br />\n<br />\n覺醒劑 呢個名好中二"},{"pid":"3a50dba8d7323be114e34e104c15b06a8dfd2e2e","tid":1188413,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:10:43.000Z","msg":"NewType<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de00e55bc3c9593045f8ea7a6a842a76befb1f1","tid":1188413,"uid":43309,"like":8,"dislike"